---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

---
<Layout title="About me">
    <div class="-mb-3 mt-16 sm:mt-32">
        <p class="text-gray-1100">On a mission to build products developers love, and along the way, teach the next generation of developers. Here's a summary of my profile so far.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="-mb-3 mt-16 sm:mt-32">
        <span class="mb-5 block font-medium sm:mb-6">Education</span>
        <ul class="my-6 ml-6 list-disc [&>li]:mt-2">
            <li class="text-gray-1100">Philadelphia, PA: MS (Master's Degree in AI&ML). Relevant Coursework: Machine Learning, Deep Learning, Computer Vision, Natural Language Processing, and Human-AI interaction</li>
            <li class="text-gray-1100">Milan, Italy: BCS (Bachelors Degree in Computer Science). Relevant Coursework: Programming, Networks and Operating Systems, Programming Languages and Databases</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="-mb-3 mt-16 sm:mt-32">
        <span class="mb-5 block font-medium sm:mb-6">Work Experiences</span>
        <ul class="my-6 ml-6 list-disc [&>li]:mt-2">
            <li>
                🇮🇹 Google, Milan, Italy (Mar. 2021 - Jan. 2022)<br/>
                <span class="text-gray-1100">
                    My task is to maintain existing services, add new features on request, develop software and update their public website as well as their social presence as needed
                </span>
            </li>
            <li>
                🇮🇹 Jan. 2020 - Jun. 2020: i-TECH Srl, Sassari, Italy:<br/>
                <span class="text-gray-1100">
                    I created a web portal that receives, displays and handles new customers, with the ability to sort, search, and integrate their workflow seamlessly into the program. It shows meaningful data regarding the customer’s origins and gives the company a tool to better direct their marketing efforts as well as their web presence among italian regions
                </span>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="-mb-3 mt-16 sm:mt-32">
        <span class="mb-5 block font-medium sm:mb-6">More</span>
        <ul class="my-6 ml-6 list-disc [&>li]:mt-2 text-gray-1100">
            <li>
                <a href="#" class="underline">Linkedin</a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="#" class="underline">CV</a>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</Layout>